      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CRISP RIDE ON (7) was popular in betting last start but disappointed when 8 lengths away in fourth (24.43). Finished second the start before. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from three starts. Has ability and looks hard to stop. MUSTANG BEACH (8) started big odds last time but hit the ground running with a strong early split, giving a sight but fading only late to finish third (24.01) at this track over 407m. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Leading player again. INDIGO BEACH (1) is mixing form and out of the placings last time but was a Grade 6 winner three starts ago and moves to Box 1 this time where she has performed well. With a good start should be able to take advantage of the rails draw. Expecting sharp improvement. CLEAR BLUE SKY (6) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
